---
title: What technologies are used in the development of Pokémon Studio?
seoDescription: The technologies used to develop Pokémon Studio
publishDate: '2022-09-15 18:05:00'
order: 0
---

Pokémon Studio is developed with **React and Electron** , which are modern and very efficient technologies. For the organisation of the project, the team uses **GitHub** (task management & versioning) and **Drive**. For the realisation of the interfaces, we're using **Figma**.

